snippet.title: Nottinghamshire Healthcare
snippet.description:
Nottinghamshire Healthcare provides integrated healthcare services, including mental health, learning disability and physical health services.

Over 9000 staff provide these services in a variety of settings, ranging from the community through to acute wards, as well as secure settings. 

www.nottinghamshirehealthcare.nhs.uk
